languages.text: Во дворцы удовольствий стекаются позабывшие Кредо грешники. Здесь может развлечься не только усталый рабочий из мануфакторума, но и пресыщенный высокорожденный.

languages.text: Many who have forgotten the Creed flock to the pleasure palaces. Here, not only can exhausted manufactorum labourers enjoy themselves, but also the most blasé of highborns.

traits.locale_text: Regular Extasiums tend to attract simple, unsophisticated lot. This district has many refined establishments that have something to offer even to the most blase noble-born guests.
